backgroundInformationList.description: Notice of Intention to Designate - 26 Millwood Road

noticeDescription:
IN THE MATTER OF THE ONTARIO HERITAGE ACT

R.S.O. 1990, CHAPTER O.18 AND

CITY OF TORONTO, PROVINCE OF ONTARIO

26 MILLWOOD ROAD

 

DEEMED WITHDRAWAL OF NOTICE OF INTENTION TO DESIGNATE THE PROPERTY

 

TAKE NOTICE that as Council for the City of Toronto did not pass the designating by-law, the notice of intention designate the property, including the lands, buildings and structures thereon, known municipally as 26 Millwood Road under Part IV, Section 29 of the Ontario Heritage Act, R.S.O. 1990, c.O.18, as amended, as a property of cultural heritage value or interest is deemed withdrawn in accordance with subsection 29(9) of the Ontario Heritage Act, R.S.O. 1990, c.O.18, as amended,.

 

This notice is being served to the Owner of the Property, the Ontario Heritage Trust, and any Objectors and Interested Persons.
title: Deemed Withdrawal of Notice of Intention to Designate - 26 Millwood Road
